          "reviewBody": "This school is known for restroom fights. Basically a low budget fight club without Brad Pitt and Edward Norton. No proper faculties for sports and weekly sports period is being taken by other subject staffs. This is not acceptable as students would remain with the pressurized mindset. I don't know about u guys but I have opened preethi pressure cook before pressure goes off and it was like Hiroshima Nagazaki. Please give justice to students.",
