          "reviewBody": "Students are not getting proper education, such a worst school I have ever seen in my life . Except one or two teachers all the other teachers are irresponsible. Maths teachers never tried to clarify the doubts . I would not like to give 1 star also . Physical education sir \" prabu \" I wish he gets dismissed.",
