          "datePublished": "2023-04-04",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My son started his schooling in park road campus. It was the best time of his life. As a parent I was very happy with the school. Later when he was shifted to mdvl campus in grade 5 , things were great until the new principal came. I waited to complete 6th standard I couldn’t run away from this school any faster. So much bullying. The principal nazreena herself body shamed my son calling him puny many times coz he is thin. My son and I regret wasting 6th grade in schram Maduravoyal.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
